## Key Architecture

### Bot State Machine
8-stage conversation flow:
1. Greeting → 2. Language → 3. Name → 4. Intent → 5. Qualifying → 6. Property shown → 7. Awaiting visit time → 8. Awaiting email → 9. Visit confirmed → 10. Handover

### AI-First Design
- AI decodes intent, code executes actions
- AI never types property facts directly
- State machine pattern with clear transitions
- Max conversation history constraint (12 messages)

### Hedged LLM Strategy
- Parallel Groq attempts
- Automatic GLM fallback on failure
- Retry mechanism with exponential backoff
- Minimizes API costs and improves reliability

### Data Architecture
- Migration-based schema (37+ migration files)
- Comprehensive indexing (50+ indexes)
- JSONB metadata for flexibility
- Conversation history limited to last 12 exchanges

### Security Model
- Row Level Security (30+ policies)
- Tenant isolation - each agent/team only sees their data
- Role-based access (service role, authenticated, public)
- Rate limiting at multiple levels
- CSP headers with HSTS

